{
    "xml": "<topic id=\"PHP85567\" outputclass=\"drug\" rev=\"1.17\" type=\"drug\" namespace=\"/drugs/alogliptin-with-metformin\" basename=\"alogliptin-with-metformin\" title=\"ALOGLIPTIN WITH METFORMIN\">\n<title>ALOGLIPTIN WITH METFORMIN</title>\n<body>\r\n<p outputclass=\"interactionsLinks\"> List of individual interactants: <xref format=\"dita\" href=\"#bnf_int_267\" namespace=\"/interactions/list-of-drug-interactions/antidiabetics/biguanides/metformin\">Metformin</xref>, <xref format=\"dita\" href=\"#bnf_int_1292\" namespace=\"/interactions/list-of-drug-interactions/antidiabetics/alogliptin\">Alogliptin</xref>\n</p>\r\n<p outputclass=\"constituentDrugs\">The properties listed below are those particular to the combination only. For the properties of the components please consider, <xref format=\"dita\" href=\"#PHP34511\" namespace=\"/drugs/alogliptin\">alogliptin</xref>, <xref format=\"dita\" href=\"#PHP4161\" namespace=\"/drugs/metformin-hydrochloride\">metformin hydrochloride</xref>.</p>\n<data name=\"vtmid\">23638611000001101</data>\n<data name=\"classifications\">\n<data name=\"classification\">\n<data name=\"drugClassification\">\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"drugClassification\" href=\"#_617518759\" title=\"Dipeptidylpeptidase-4 inhibitors (gliptins)\">Dipeptidylpeptidase-4 inhibitors (gliptins)</xref>\n</data>\n</data>\r\n<data name=\"classification\">\n<data name=\"drugClassification\">\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"drugClassification\" href=\"#_709441655\" title=\"Biguanides\">Biguanides</xref>\n</data>\n</data>\n</data>\n<data name=\"primaryDomainOfEffect\">\n<data name=\"domainOfEffect\">  </data>\n</data>\r\n</body>\n<topic id=\"PHP86158\" outputclass=\"indicationsAndDose\" rev=\"1.15\" parent=\"/drugs/alogliptin-with-metformin\">\n<title>Indications and dose</title>\n<body>\n<section outputclass=\"indicationAndDoseGroup\">\n<sectiondiv outputclass=\"therapeuticIndications\">\n<p outputclass=\"therapeuticIndication\">Type 2 diabetes mellitus not controlled by metformin alone or by metformin in combination with either pioglitazone or insulin</p>\n</sectiondiv>\n<p outputclass=\"routesOfAdministration\">By mouth</p>\n<ul outputclass=\"patientGroups\">\n<li outputclass=\"patientGroup adult\">\n<p>Adult</p>\n<p>1&#8239;tablet twice daily, based on patient's current metformin dose.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</body>\n</topic>\n<topic id=\"PHP86159\" outputclass=\"interactions\" rev=\"1.13\" parent=\"/drugs/alogliptin-with-metformin\">\n<title>Interactions</title>\n<body>\n<section outputclass=\"general\">\n<sectiondiv>\n<p>Dose of concomitant sulfonylurea or insulin may need to be reduced.</p>\n<p>Caution with use in combination with both metformin and pioglitazone&#8212;risk of hypoglycaemia (dose of metformin or pioglitazone may need to be reduced).</p>\n</sectiondiv>\n</section>\n</body>\n</topic>\n<topic id=\"PHP85567-medicinalForms\" outputclass=\"medicinalForms\" parent=\"/drugs/alogliptin-with-metformin\">\n<title>Medicinal forms</title>\n<body>\n<section outputclass=\"licensingVariationStatement\">\n<p>There can be variation in the licensing of different medicines containing the same drug.</p>\n</section>\n</body>\n</topic>\n<parents>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"drugs\" href=\"#drugs\" title=\"Drugs\" namespace=\"/drugs\">Drugs</xref>\n</parents>\n<children>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"medicinalForm\" href=\"#PHP92215\" title=\"Tablet\" namespace=\"/drugs/alogliptin-with-metformin/tablet\">Tablet</xref>\n</children>\n<backlinks>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"drugClassifications\" href=\"#PHP106980\" namespace=\"/drug-classifications\" title=\"Drug classifications\" count=\"2\" rel=\"backlink\">Drug classifications</xref>\n</backlinks>\n<links>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"interaction\" href=\"#bnf_int_267\" namespace=\"/interactions/list-of-drug-interactions/antidiabetics/biguanides/metformin\" title=\"Metformin\" count=\"1\" rel=\"link\">Metformin</xref>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"interaction\" href=\"#bnf_int_1292\" namespace=\"/interactions/list-of-drug-interactions/antidiabetics/alogliptin\" title=\"Alogliptin\" count=\"1\" rel=\"link\">Alogliptin</xref>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"drug\" href=\"#PHP34511\" namespace=\"/drugs/alogliptin\" title=\"ALOGLIPTIN\" count=\"1\" rel=\"link\">ALOGLIPTIN</xref>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"drug\" href=\"#PHP4161\" namespace=\"/drugs/metformin-hydrochloride\" title=\"METFORMIN HYDROCHLORIDE\" count=\"1\" rel=\"link\">METFORMIN HYDROCHLORIDE</xref>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"#drugs\" href=\"#drugs\" namespace=\"/drugs\" title=\"Drugs\" count=\"1\" rel=\"link\">Drugs</xref>\n<xref format=\"dita\" scope=\"local\" type=\"medicinalForm\" href=\"#PHP92215\" namespace=\"/drugs/alogliptin-with-metformin/tablet\" title=\"Tablet\" count=\"1\" rel=\"link\">Tablet</xref>\n</links>\n</topic>",
